      "body" : "I think the persistent CWalletDb object here is just there to prevent a flush to disk in between every added transaction, for performance reasons. Based on earlier pull requests by @pstratem around this, I think he intends to re-introduce a single CWalletDb* inside CWallet rather than reopening one all the time, after cleaning things up. Perhaps that will need to be done in the same PR, though?",
